import styles from './UserList.module.css' import { store } from '../../app/store' import { UserType } from '../../types' const UserList = () => { const users: UserType[] = store.getState().usersReducers console.log(users) const usersTableRows: JSX.Element[] = [] // eslint-disable-next-line array-callback-return users.map(user => { usersTableRows.push( {user.name} {user.surname} {user.e_mail} ) }) return (
{usersTableRows}
Name Surame Email
) } export default UserList
